original_title: AKB48 リクエストアワー セットリストベスト100 2010
overview: The AKB48 Request Hour Setlist Best 100 2010 (AKB48 リクエストアワー セットリストベスト100 2010) was held from January 21 to January 24, 2010 at Shibuya AX. Fans made their voices heard by voting for their favorite AKB48/SKE48/SDN48 original songs.
title: AKB48 Request Hour Setlist Best 100 2010
